title: _V173 Page Management
content:
This page, created by me ([[*user V173]]), manages my posts across the Site via ListPage modules.

This page is normally hidden.

[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=]]
+++ ALL PAGES
[[/=]]
-----
[[module ListPages separate="no" created_by="V173" category="*" pagetype="*"]]
@@ @@
[[table class="wiki-content-table"]]
[[row]]
[[hcell colspan="3"]] (%%index%%/%%total%%) %%title_linked%% (%%category%%) [[/hcell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell]] **By** [[*user %%created_by%%]] [[/cell]]
[[cell]] **Created on:** %%created_at%% [[/cell]]
[[cell]] **Last Updated:** %%updated_at%% by [[*user %%updated_by%%]] [[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[hcell colspan="3"]]
[[=]]
[[collapsible show="More Info"]]
[[/=]]
[[table class="wiki-content-table"]]
[[row]]
[[cell]] Revisions: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%revisions%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[cell]] Comments: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%comments%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[cell]] Last commented: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%commented_at%% by [[*user %%commented_by%%]][[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell]] Rating: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%rating%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[cell]] Votes: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%rating_votes%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[cell]] Percent: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%rating_percent%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell]] Size: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%size%% characters[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[cell]] Parent: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%parent_title_linked%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[cell]] Children: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%children%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell colspan="3"]] Tags: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%tags_linked%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell colspan="3"]] Hidden Tags: [[span style="font-weight:normal;"]]%%_tags_linked%%[[/span]] [[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[/table]]
[[/collapsible]]
[[/hcell]]
[[/row]]
[[/table]]
@@ @@
-----
[[/module]]
[[/div]]
author: V173
